snippet.textDisplay: please don't ruin jazz by mixing it with rock...the fusion did not work well with the heavy guitar solo. if using an electric guitar was that necessary, I'd have suggested a more a bluesy slick. plain acoustics, piano and harmonica. I feel sad every time I hear in bts videos "chords bohot kam hain", kyun aik acha ganna kam chords kay saath nahin ban sakta? and if no, then its sad that your perception of art is complicating things rather than keeping it simple and straight forward that just hits the feels at the right spot.
